y? Book through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a> as they work with local car rental companies and the price includes all insurances. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"tuscany road trip siena\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tuscany road trip siena\" class=\"wp-image-14018 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/tuscany-road-trip-siena-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135724\/t