    <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you&#x2019;re looking to avoid mass-tourism, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/umbria-italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">visit incredible Umbria<\/a> (Tuscany&#x2019;s neighbouring region)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/road-trip-tuscany-landscape.jpg\" alt=\"road trip tuscany landscape\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"road trip tuscany landscape\" class=\"wp-image-14026 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135706\/road-trip-tuscany-landscape.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135706\/road-trip-tuscany-landscape-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135706\/road-trip-tuscany-landscape-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135706\/road-trip-tuscany-landscape-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135706\/road-trip-tuscany-landscape-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135706\/road-trip-tuscany-landscape-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135706\/road-trip-tuscany-landscape-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135706\/road-trip-tuscany