ing dip in the hot pools before hitting the road towards Rome, the final destination of the Tuscany road trip. Driving over the hills takes around 3 hours to reach Rome.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/italy\/rome\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Best Things to do in Rome, Italy (opens in a new tab)\">Best Things to do in Rome, Italy<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/things-to-do-rome.jpg\" alt=\"things to do rome\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"304\" alt=\"things to do rome\" class=\"wp-image-13940 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135829\/things-to-do-rome.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135829\/things-to-do-rome-300x203.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135829\/things-to-do-rome-600x406.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135829\/things-to-do-rome-450x304.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135829\/things-to-do-rome-800x541.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135829\/things-to-do-rome-1080x731.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-cont